function Get-AnyStackOrphanedState {
    <#
    .SYNOPSIS
        Finds orphaned VMs.
    .DESCRIPTION
        Checks Runtime.ConnectionState.
    .PARAMETER Server
        vCenter Server hostname or VIServer object. Uses active connection if omitted.
    .EXAMPLE
        PS> Get-AnyStackOrphanedState
    .OUTPUTS
        PSCustomObject
